data.description: Welcome Home To Cadence and all its amenities. This Home Features 3 Bedrooms, 3 Bath, and a Loft, upgraded cabinetry, an oversized Kitchen Island with Granite countertops, an under-mount sink, stainless steel appliances, updated luxury vinyl planks flooring, and ceiling fans. The low-maintenance backyard is complete with pavers, a raised planter, synthetic grass, a covered patio, and a covered balcony off the primary suite. Perfect for entertaining friends and family all year long.  Just a quick walk to the Cadence community area which includes walking trails, park areas, multiple playgrounds, splash pad, pickle ball courts, community pool, and the centerpiece lake area! Be sure to view the floorplan, pictures, and virtual tour.
